:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"【背水收料！區選可疑車輛觀察計劃🕵🏿】<br />\n<br />\n‼️唔好意思臨急臨忙要大家幫手‼️<br />\n<br />\n請大家今日出門投票時留意自己區有無旅遊巴、可疑車輛嘅蹤跡，背水團隊希望用嚟cross-check我哋嘅data，睇下有無一啲可疑／懷疑種票情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n由於要處理嘅資料眾多，麻煩咁多位手足幫手影低佢，再填妥以下google form。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/DZnuyZUfsztcgXUA9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FDZnuyZUfsztcgXUA9&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=846f3d5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/DZnuyZUfsztcgXUA9</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝各位，今日見🙏<br />\n<br />\np.s. 係啊種票情況次次有，但請勿對荒謬習以為常。"},{"pid":"ac8d6b001addafbeba57f150d23a543ef4e9dc99","tid":1749273,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9dc1a88e99ee50fc252f09354afd4f838d7d9d2","tid":1749273,"uid":47955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bb064866d487eeed4b0dbd1bf5b6d72e5bb231d","tid":1749273,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72c97da2b0254906b17a4a745bc5a4d07974dcec","tid":1749273,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b9ebe21b19841c7b57704e4b6044601578707b77","tid":1749273,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e4b1bcdd98fbebaea2f2c27f868b8290aba41f93","tid":1749273,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0dccbbf08eaa12d4c17fc189bdc3782be464209c","tid":1749273,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:22:29.000Z","msg":"有乜疑似干預選舉情況<br />\n拍片/相&mdash;》<br />\n<br />\n「選舉觀察計劃」報料熱線 Election Observation Hotline<br />\nTelegram: @hotline19hkeop<br />\nWhatsApp: +85297424472<br />\n又或者報料俾傳媒記者（蘋果丶有線丶立場）<br />